  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One person injured in bear attack in Puliankulam",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vavuniya - A young man has been admitted to the Vavuniya hospital after being attacked by a bear in Puliankulam forest area.",
        "Yesterday afternoon (17) when a group of eight people went to the forest area of \u200b\u200bPuliankulam Kachchakkodi area to collect honey, the youth was attacked by a bear and the youth was seriously injured.",
        "After this, the said youth was rescued by others from the area and taken to Puliankulam Hospital.",
        "Nadarasa Dharmarasa (33 years old) from Pulyankulam area was the target of the bear attack and was seriously injured."
      ],
